        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JL for a flower of <hi rend="italic">Bolbophyllum</hi>, a genus that puzzles him.</p>  
<p>Recent work has convinced him a number of orchids are male. Points out that JL [in <hi rend="italic">The vegetable kingdom</hi> (1846), pp. 177–8] "accidentally misquoted" R. H. Schomburgk on this point.</p> 
        </abstract>
